column5: Cryptic,  What's the PM about.  C,mon  Why so secretive.  What are you hiding.  Think you're pretty clever,  don't you.   Is it about meatloaf? GCD? skin care?   I'm sending my own PM's.  Right now.  To people.

Hey brother, Just checked my PM's folder.... I have not received one today. But I would like you to send one and ignore the other fools that posted before me LOL   Just my 0.02 cents worth <-- Thats for you Snag  Gerritt.
I'll get you for that.  2 cented, secret PM man
